{
  "stem": "4513.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were in a camp-- Houndstone Barracks, I think it was, in-- in Yeovil.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The thing that amazed me was we went-- we got there in the middle of the night.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were awakened that next morning by British youngsters, boys and girls running all over the camp waking us up, saying hello to us.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was saying, how'd these people get into a military camp?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they were, and the people were just-- they were outrageous.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were just very, very nice to us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that was the first time that I can remember in my life, outside of Daniel, that I had a-- just-- just that kind of relationship with white youngsters.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was just a different world.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was very foreign to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't know what to suspect-- expect.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I thought, you know, be careful 'cause you still don't know what these people are gonna do to you.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know what that was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But see, you have to know that when I was in high school, every day, every week, we had auditorium.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they would bring in somebody who was well-renowned in the black-- an artist or a painter or a philosopher or a professor, and they would talk to us.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But everybody had the same theme.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "If you're gonna make it in this country, you gotta be better than white folk doing it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You gotta exceed what white folks can do.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that-- Purdue caused me a lot of trouble and that caused me a lot of trouble at Purdue.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because I couldn't be better than all those kids.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And now I'm dealing-- you know, it's one thing to say that when you're in high school, and you're not competing with anybody white.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
